document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Louise Lake Project in North America dated July 2006.pdf
document.description: This report provides an independent and CIM-compliant resource estimate for the copper-gold-molybdenum-silver deposit at the Louise Lake Property in British Columbia, summarizing exploration history, geological setting, and resource classification.
